      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YUMALI (2) has a strong record this trip with seven wins and four placings from 17 starts. Missed the frame latest (22.87) when seventh over 395m at Murray Bridge in a Grade 3/4/5. Looks suited here and rates on top. JUKEBOX DUKE (1) was in the minor money with a strong 22.79, finishing third in a Free For All at Gawler last start. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. TRADING HALT (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (23.47) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here winning five races. Has ability and is one of the better chances. HIGH CUBE (4) took up a forward position and go the job done last time out. That form reads well.",
